{"tid":1858970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢臨時政府...... 反了反了","createTime":"2020-02-03T04:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T11:58:19.000Z","uid":57073,"like":350,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b7664265925c064135d89a9c597adc1515f1ce","tid":1858970,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"武汉临时政府命令，所有武汉市的官员、湖北省的官员，脱离中国共产党的指挥，通过公开或秘密渠道向本临时政府报到，看守现有岗位职责，服从本临时政府的指令，并静候改组。<br />\n本临时政府开始运作，筹组国事会议，筹拟武汉临时约法，筹办由全体年满18岁武汉居民、湖北居民参与投票的普选，建立民选议会和<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wsnGC4GYsKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwsnGC4GYsKI&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=308ab92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wsnGC4GYsKI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/ShengXue_ca/status/1223849972501749760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FShengXue_ca%2Fstatus%2F1223849972501749760&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V4oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=4f420c16\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/ShengXue_ca/status/1223849972501749760</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7087767f44f74b8fff2c83b33176e375ab2b791","tid":1858970,"uid":191926,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"無軍火 無用"},{"pid":"fbe0053a47240136133cf00c3b7cc1d0208a68e0","tid":1858970,"uid":57073,"like":238,"dislike":2,"score":236,"quote":{"pid":"c7087767f44f74b8fff2c83b33176e375ab2b791","tid":1858970,"uid":191926,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"無軍火 無用"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"有移動化武"},{"pid":"d9d925f30e0da288424fa85349a7c8af544ed093","tid":1858970,"uid":53857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbe0053a47240136133cf00c3b7cc1d0208a68e0","tid"